# GitHub Actions secrets — Crypto Pay (photospheremedia/Crypto-Pay)
#
# NEVER commit real values. Store values in GitHub → Settings → Secrets and variables → Actions.
#
# Check what's set (names only):
#   gh secret list -R photospheremedia/Crypto-Pay
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 1. GITHUB ACTIONS SECRETS (CI/CD only — not used at Vercel runtime)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# Secret name              | Workflow              | Where to get the value
# -------------------------|-----------------------|------------------------------------------
# SUPABASE_ACCESS_TOKEN    | supabase.yml          | https://supabase.com/dashboard/account/tokens (sbp_...)
# SUPABASE_PROJECT_REF     | supabase.yml          | usbxwewohpsbjwiuazpf
# RESEND_API_KEY           | supabase.yml (opt.)   | https://resend.com/api-keys (re_...)
# VERCEL_TOKEN             | vercel.yml (opt.)     | https://vercel.com/account/tokens
# VERCEL_ORG_ID            | vercel.yml (opt.)     | .vercel/project.json after pnpm vercel:link
# VERCEL_PROJECT_ID        | vercel.yml (opt.)     | .vercel/project.json after pnpm vercel:link
# PORKBUN_API_KEY          | dns-vercel.yml        | Porkbun → Account → API Access
# PORKBUN_SECRET_API_KEY   | dns-vercel.yml        | Porkbun → Account → API Access
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL | vercel.yml (PR test)  | apps/portal/.env.local — Playwright
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY | vercel.yml (PR)  | Supabase Dashboard → API
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY | vercel.yml (PR)     | Supabase Dashboard → API (server)
#
# Bootstrap (repo admin):
#   pnpm supabase:secrets
#   pnpm vercel:secrets
#   pnpm portal:secrets
#   pnpm porkbun:secrets
#
# Minimum CI: SUPABASE_ACCESS_TOKEN, SUPABASE_PROJECT_REF
# Portal deploy: Vercel GitHub app OR VERCEL_TOKEN + VERCEL_ORG_ID + VERCEL_PROJECT_ID
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 2. LOCAL GITIGNORED FILES
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# .env.supabase            | SUPABASE_ACCESS_TOKEN, SUPABASE_PROJECT_REF
# apps/portal/.env.local   | App runtime keys
# .env.vercel              | VERCEL_TOKEN (pnpm vercel:secrets)
# .env.porkbun             | PORKBUN_API_KEY, PORKBUN_SECRET_API_KEY
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 3. VERCEL PROJECT ENV (production — NOT in GitHub Secrets)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# pnpm vercel:env-sync  (from apps/portal/.env.local)
#
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL, NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY, SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY
# NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=https://cryptopay.sale
# RESEND_API_KEY, EMAIL_FROM, EMAIL_REPLY_TO, ADMIN_REVIEW_EMAIL
# NEXT_PUBLIC_TURNSTILE_SITE_KEY, TURNSTILE_SECRET_KEY, GROQ_API_KEY
#
# Full template: apps/portal/.env.example
